quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  107,4,"So woe to those who pray"
  107,5,"[But] who are heedless of their prayer{1} -",footnotes:1:[i.e., the hypocrites who are unconcerned if they miss prayers when no one sees them.]
  107,6,"Those who make show [of their deeds]"
  108,1,"Indeed, We have granted you, [O Muḥammad], al-Kawthar."
  108,2,"So pray to your Lord and offer sacrifice [to Him alone]."
  108,3,"Indeed, your enemy is the one cut off.{1}",footnotes:1:[From all good in this world and the Hereafter.]
